    - target: {fileID: 6610395829144855160, guid: 1fe3254925087564a998ec9ad7ad7b27, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'This uses the PowerScalar Custom Property, which applies a power on
        the value before packing, and reverts it after unpacking, so as to bias precision
        towards low or high value range.


        Here it controls the material
        color, with a Power of 3, this provides much more precision between 0 and
        0.5, than between 0.5 and 1.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8791987005405927867, guid: 1fe3254925087564a998ec9ad7ad7b27, type: 3}
